{"tid":1630649,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地係咪應該俾黨鐵一個死線","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:58.000Z","uid":2235,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e020590130fad039a71c9822fe6e60d4a23c6f","tid":1630649,"uid":2235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:10:27.000Z","msg":"見到勇武裝修黨鐵係十分治癒，黨鐵<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自作自受</span></span></strong>，但永無止境咁裝修<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>未必達到最大效益。</strong></span></span><br />\n原因有幾個：<br />\n一、黨鐵唔開會令到好多人出唔到黎示威（今日好多巴士係總站已經爆左，好多人想出到出唔到）<br />\n二、國際層面未必睇到我地裝修嘅理據，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">萬一影響人權法通過的話就制裁唔到黑警同班垃圾高官</span></strong></span>，始終好多外國人睇野好表面，睇片睇圖就算數，並非個個都仔細咁睇/聽我地解釋，正如大家睇其他國家嘅政事都未必好透澈了解哂<br />\n三、香港人真係好Q鍾意番工，依家唔係所有交通都唔得，姐係公司會繼續要大家番工啦，無可否認，塞車、排長龍唔多唔少都會產生怨氣<br />\n<br />\n我並<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係建議大家唔裝修，而係為裝修定下停止嘅條件</span></span></strong>，潛在嘅好處有幾個：<br />\n一、部份市民嘅怨氣會轉去唔答應示威者合理訴求嘅黨鐵<br />\n二、可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">釋除國際疑惑</span></span></strong>，順便reiterate 我地裝修黨鐵嘅原因，recall 番國際當時黨鐵721 831 出賣示威者淪為黑警私家車，勇武先要裝修，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將焦點落番喺黨鐵惡行上面</span></span></strong><br />\n三、始終我地目標唔係影響民生，裝修港鐵唔係為左發洩，係話俾黨鐵聽背叛香港人嘅後果，我地應該<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用裝修做籌碼，黎bargain 對運動有利嘅野</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至於有咩條件，我見網上亦有人討論過，我諗最起碼都有呢幾個（歡迎大家題意）：<br />\n一、發放uncut, unedited 嘅 831 CCTV<br />\n二、不再隨意因警方要求停站<br />\n<br />\n假如黨鐵不回應，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>相信大家嘅怒火不會熄滅，裝修行動不會停</strong></span></span>。萬一黨鐵回應訴求，咁我地將佢降級為裝飾亦合情合理？大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />贊成向黨鐵提出停裝修條件<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做黎都無用<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n香港人，反抗！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a54b9888e722521525e638ba463536b6aa348ee2","tid":1630649,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bebd8e6b201844b729d35c608e09878636da2fec","tid":1630649,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"發夢？<br />\n黨鐵肯企手足一邊就唔叫黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n佢即日禁狗入港鐵範圍同唔停駛咪放佢一馬<br />\n<br />\n唔係盞手足危險"},{"pid":"0f98a0f2493ca6990ba4e009227a2ac680a8fa45","tid":1630649,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"邊個大大聲話集中<br />\n<br />\n鞭屍時間<br />\n<br />\n集中撚答到我問題，先好叫人出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"52e779fe95b8181762169158d7bfb86eaf696c65","tid":1630649,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"冇死線啊，每日都係行動日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f04E6d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff04E6d0.png&h=0ada5c0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"751442dcd7492b36c818a449c7e15e77807d5db8","tid":1630649,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"再唔交片就全部站同佢玩水舞間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b78da67928f06584fc7c7d1c89e9dfbfb3bb7b5","tid":1630649,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:20:45.000Z","msg":"黨鐵<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">春袋</span></span>係<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控制室</span></span><br />\n好多車站開唔到都係因為控制室維修唔到<br />\n因為所有訊號同指示都係由控制室傳達"},{"pid":"072d2c4042dbfb8e4edee61d0862b4b984a68429","tid":1630649,"uid":2235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bebd8e6b201844b729d35c608e09878636da2fec","tid":1630649,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"發夢？<br />\n黨鐵肯企手足一邊就唔叫黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n佢即日禁狗入港鐵範圍同唔停駛咪放佢一馬<br />\n<br />\n唔係盞手足危險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"黨鐵7成股份係垃圾政府，但唔係要佢企係示威者呢邊，係要同佢地bargain，依家垃圾MTR日日停，佢地班高層實瀨哂尿，any policy possible to lessen the damage to MTR must under their consideration, if they refuse, it won't hurt us but the world will better understand why the protesters will renovate"},{"pid":"a0b29f9334d59b9b373243a8006ccf5a238a48e1","tid":1630649,"uid":2235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52e779fe95b8181762169158d7bfb86eaf696c65","tid":1630649,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"冇死線啊，每日都係行動日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f04E6d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff04E6d0.png&h=0ada5c0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贊成，假如黨鐵做到嘅咪停囉"},{"pid":"5d1e39ccee1583b8505e303d4f318342c45b8318","tid":1630649,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:25:35.000Z","msg":"超級讚成"},{"pid":"3b94a4e6a368459b9d8d9b9ac447fbeeb6f5082e","tid":1630649,"uid":2235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d1e39ccee1583b8505e303d4f318342c45b8318","tid":1630649,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:25:35.000Z","msg":"超級讚成"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"香港人點睇唔係最緊要，但國際層面一定要留意，人權法未過架，當然過左就另計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a